00:12:07,960 --> 00:12:08,720
tell me now.

284
00:12:08,960 --> 00:12:10,200
Princess Fuqing's eye condition

285
00:12:10,960 --> 00:12:12,400
is likely caused
by Nanwu's venomous insect.

286
00:12:12,600 --> 00:12:13,160
Are you certain?

287
00:12:13,400 --> 00:12:14,000
Almost.

288
00:12:14,560 --> 00:12:15,240
If we follow

289
00:12:15,480 --> 00:12:16,080
the trail

290
00:12:16,080 --> 00:12:17,200
of Princess Fuqing's blindness,

291
00:12:17,560 --> 00:12:18,120
we might be able

292
00:12:18,520 --> 00:12:20,040
to find the Nanwu woman

293
00:12:20,160 --> 00:12:20,760
hidden in the palace.

294
00:12:21,360 --> 00:12:22,640
His Majesty has always been biased

295
00:12:22,680 --> 00:12:23,720
toward Princess Royal.

296
00:12:23,960 --> 00:12:25,280
The only way we can truly be safe is

297
00:12:25,280 --> 00:12:26,720
by gathering evidence
that proves Princess Royal is colluding

298
00:12:27,200 --> 00:12:28,280
with Nanwu.

299
00:12:28,520 --> 00:12:29,440
Princess Fuqing

300
00:12:29,720 --> 00:12:30,320
is clearly

301
00:12:30,320 --> 00:12:31,480
a kind and reasonable young lady.

302
00:12:31,920 --> 00:12:33,920
To be blind in her prime…

303
00:12:34,880 --> 00:12:35,520
If we can cure her,

304
00:12:35,680 --> 00:12:37,280
we will be doing a good deed

305
00:12:37,720 --> 00:12:39,000
as well.

306
00:12:41,160 --> 00:12:41,840
It'll be fine.

307
00:12:42,280 --> 00:12:43,880
It's just three days. Please?

308
00:12:45,160 --> 00:12:45,600
All right.

309
00:12:46,320 --> 00:12:47,800
I'll pick you up in three days.

310
00:12:50,880 --> 00:12:51,760
Your Majesty,

311
00:12:52,360 --> 00:12:55,320
was the mole at the corner
of Princess Fuqing's eye there

312
00:12:56,000 --> 00:12:57,160
since birth,

313
00:12:57,800 --> 00:12:58,800
or did it only appear

314
00:12:58,800 --> 00:12:59,640
after she lost her sight?

315
00:13:00,040 --> 00:13:01,440
Fuqing was born without a mole

316
00:13:02,080 --> 00:13:03,520
at the corner of her eye.

317
00:13:04,560 --> 00:13:05,400
Now that I think about it,

318
00:13:06,240 --> 00:13:07,240
that mole only appeared

319
00:13:07,320 --> 00:13:08,640
after she developed

320
00:13:08,680 --> 00:13:09,680
her eye condition.

321
00:13:12,480 --> 00:13:13,680
Has the color of this mole

322
00:13:13,960 --> 00:13:15,200
gradually darkened

323
00:13:15,640 --> 00:13:18,240
over the years?

324
00:13:18,480 --> 00:13:19,240
Yes.

325
00:13:20,600 --> 00:13:22,600
But isn't that normal?

326
00:13:23,800 --> 00:13:24,640
That's precisely why

327
00:13:25,640 --> 00:13:26,920
such a small mole

328
00:13:28,400 --> 00:13:29,960
wouldn't arouse suspicion.

329
00:13:41,880 --> 00:13:42,680
Leave us.

330
00:13:49,040 --> 00:13:49,960
What are you suggesting?

331
00:13:51,600 --> 00:13:52,600
Is Fuqing's mole

332
00:13:52,720 --> 00:13:53,720
related to her blindness?

333
00:13:54,040 --> 00:13:54,800
I once read about it

334
00:13:54,800 --> 00:13:56,000
in an ancient text.

335
00:13:56,640 --> 00:13:57,680
It's an insect known as the "Blind Bug."

336
00:13:58,000 --> 00:13:59,400
It can reside in the human eye,

337
00:13:59,800 --> 00:14:01,000
blocking the meridians

338
00:14:01,080 --> 00:14:02,080
and shutting the eye's sensory pathways,

339
00:14:02,200 --> 00:14:03,400
causing permanent blindness.

340
00:14:03,880 --> 00:14:05,160
Your Highness's "mole"

341
00:14:05,200 --> 00:14:06,160
is not actually a mole.

342
00:14:07,360 --> 00:14:08,360
It's an insect infestation.

343
00:14:08,560 --> 00:14:09,600
Really?

344
00:14:11,800 --> 00:14:12,600
Are you saying

345
00:14:13,320 --> 00:14:14,240
that my daughter's blindness

346
00:14:14,320 --> 00:14:16,040
was not caused
by the brightness of the sky lanterns?

347
00:14:16,560 --> 00:14:17,320
Could the bug

348
00:14:18,280 --> 00:14:19,320
have entered Fuqing's eye

349
00:14:19,360 --> 00:14:20,320
on its own?

350
00:14:20,800 --> 00:14:21,440
This type of bug

351
00:14:21,560 --> 00:14:22,840
must be carefully cultivated

352
00:14:23,520 --> 00:14:24,840
before it can survive in the human eye.

353
00:14:25,680 --> 00:14:27,000
You're telling me

354
00:14:27,520 --> 00:14:28,880
someone deliberately plotted

355
00:14:28,880 --> 00:14:30,240
to make Fuqing blind?

356
00:14:30,840 --> 00:14:31,280
Yes.

357
00:14:39,000 --> 00:14:40,560
Since joining the palace,

358
00:14:41,960 --> 00:14:44,000
I have never felt jealousy
or resentment.

359
00:14:44,880 --> 00:14:47,080
I have never made enemies
among the concubines,

360
00:14:48,440 --> 00:14:50,440
nor have I treated

361
00:14:52,120 --> 00:14:54,520
any of the palace maids
or eunuchs harshly.

362
00:14:55,960 --> 00:14:58,040
I have done everything I could
to be kind.

363
00:15:00,520 --> 00:15:02,040
Why would someone still want

364
00:15:02,040 --> 00:15:03,400
to harm my daughter?

365
