367
00:15:12,800 --> 00:15:15,520
Who would do something so cruel?

368
00:15:16,360 --> 00:15:16,920
Your Majesty,

369
00:15:17,720 --> 00:15:19,000
we must find

370
00:15:19,000 --> 00:15:19,600
the one responsible.

371
00:15:20,120 --> 00:15:21,160
If we find the culprit,

372
00:15:21,400 --> 00:15:22,880
there is a chance
Her Highness' eyesight

373
00:15:23,560 --> 00:15:24,680
can be restored.

374
00:15:31,080 --> 00:15:31,680
Your Highness.

375
00:15:32,200 --> 00:15:34,400
Jiang Si was punished when she visited

376
00:15:34,760 --> 00:15:35,640
Imperial Concubine Xian yesterday.

377
00:15:36,200 --> 00:15:37,680
Today, she accompanied Prince Yan

378
00:15:37,720 --> 00:15:39,480
to visit Empress Di

379
00:15:40,080 --> 00:15:42,400
