to learn palace etiquette.

380
00:15:43,720 --> 00:15:45,560
Well, she's certainly adaptive.

381
00:15:46,400 --> 00:15:48,120
She knows Imperial Concubine Xian
won't support her,

382
00:15:48,480 --> 00:15:49,880
