to curry the Empress's favor.

383
00:15:50,720 --> 00:15:51,520
What a pity.

384
00:15:51,960 --> 00:15:53,280
She chose the wrong person to rely on.

385
00:15:56,240 --> 00:15:58,640
Return to the palace
and deliver a message.

386
00:15:59,280 --> 00:16:02,080
Tell the Nanwu woman
to take care of her as soon as possible.

387
00:16:02,800 --> 00:16:03,400
Yes.

