00:16:20,960 --> 00:16:22,600
is one of my old attendants?

396
00:16:23,680 --> 00:16:26,480
This bug is difficult
to sustain in the human eye.

397
00:16:27,240 --> 00:16:28,200
It requires careful nurturing

398
00:16:28,200 --> 00:16:29,200
over time.

399
00:16:29,840 --> 00:16:30,800
Princess Fuqing

400
00:16:30,920 --> 00:16:32,400
lost her sight

401
00:16:32,400 --> 00:16:33,200
shortly before Your Majesty
became the Empress.

402
00:16:33,800 --> 00:16:34,720
So, I believe

403
00:16:35,240 --> 00:16:36,320
the culprit must have come

404
00:16:36,320 --> 00:16:37,280
