00:17:03,600 --> 00:17:04,599
Your Majesty,
please don't jump to conclusions.

417
00:17:04,960 --> 00:17:06,359
This is merely my speculation.

418
00:17:07,079 --> 00:17:08,520
It couldn't be them.

