00:18:16,680 --> 00:18:17,480
It is quite high.

445
00:18:18,240 --> 00:18:18,920
Let me give it a try.

446
00:18:37,520 --> 00:18:38,120
I got it!

447
00:18:41,960 --> 00:18:43,120
I got the kite down. Look.

448
00:18:44,560 --> 00:18:45,200
Is it damaged?

449
00:18:45,840 --> 00:18:46,760
No, it's fine.

450
00:18:47,600 --> 00:18:48,920
Only the string snapped.

451
00:18:49,240 --> 00:18:50,400
Your Highness, please hold it.

452
00:18:50,800 --> 00:18:51,680
I'll tie the string

453
00:18:51,760 --> 00:18:52,800
back together.

454
00:18:54,760 --> 00:18:55,360
Did you fix it?

455
00:18:56,160 --> 00:18:56,680
Yes, it's reattached.

456
00:18:57,440 --> 00:18:58,120
That's good.

457
00:18:59,520 --> 00:19:01,360
If only everything in this world

458
00:19:01,560 --> 00:19:03,040
could be mended as easily

459
00:19:03,120 --> 00:19:04,600
as a broken kite string.

