479
00:19:49,160 --> 00:19:51,840
one must appoint the worthy
without avoiding personal ties.

480
00:19:52,800 --> 00:19:53,240
Your Majesty.

481
00:19:54,160 --> 00:19:55,320
Prince Yan emerged as a top candidate

482
00:19:55,800 --> 00:19:57,240
