and offers her unique insights.

518
00:21:23,600 --> 00:21:24,600
Her wit is admirable.

519
00:21:25,000 --> 00:21:25,960
Think again.

520
00:21:26,560 --> 00:21:27,440
Beyond academics,

521
00:21:27,680 --> 00:21:29,080
