522
00:21:35,320 --> 00:21:35,720
Yes.

523
00:21:36,840 --> 00:21:38,880
Despite her noble status,

524
00:21:39,280 --> 00:21:41,040
Her Highness has no airs of arrogance.

525
00:21:41,600 --> 00:21:42,560
She treats the palace servants

526
00:21:42,760 --> 00:21:43,880
with kindness and generosity.

527
00:21:44,120 --> 00:21:45,560
She possesses a benevolent heart.

528
00:21:45,800 --> 00:21:46,600
Is that all?

529
00:21:48,360 --> 00:21:48,800
Yes.

530
00:21:58,360 --> 00:21:59,840
The kite is flying!

531
00:22:02,880 --> 00:22:03,600
It's up in the air!

532
00:22:04,640 --> 00:22:05,040
Slow down!

533
00:22:05,040 --> 00:22:05,680
Princess Fuqing!

