Minister Zhen,

543
00:22:39,480 --> 00:22:41,680
what do you think?

544
00:22:45,240 --> 00:22:45,800
Your Majesty.

545
00:22:46,880 --> 00:22:49,200
I do not have a suitable suitor

546
00:22:49,200 --> 00:22:50,000
